===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Allwinner]] A20 @1.0GHz Dual-core ARM (Cortex-A7) *GPU: Mali-400MP2 @600MHz (supports OpenGL ES 2.0) *Memory: 1GB (DDR3) SDRAM (shared with GPU) *Storage: SD card (max. 32GB) / SATA 2.0 slot *USB: 2x USB 2.0 (Host), 1x USB 2.0 (OTG) ports *LAN: 1x GbE (RJ45) port
